Privacy Policy
Effective Date:
July 11, 2024
Thank you for using Hookify. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy outlines how we handle your data.
Data Collection
We do not collect, store, or share any personal data from our users. Our app is designed to function without requiring any user data to be collected.
Data Usage
All data you input into the app, such as webhook URLs and messages, is sent directly to Discord servers securely over HTTPS. We do not retain or store any of this information.
Security
We use industry-standard security measures to ensure that your data is transmitted securely. All communications between our app and Discord servers are encrypted using HTTPS.
Changes to This Policy
We may update our privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the effective date will be updated accordingly.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at
mason@multision.dev
.
By using our app, you agree to the terms outlined in this privacy policy.